title: Treasures of China by Annette Juliano (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Treasures of China
Richard Marek Publishers | 1984 | ISBN 0399901051 | English | 196 pages | PDF | 46 MB


This is a stunning photographic journey through more than 360 of China's natural and cultural treasures. Awesome photos and details. It shows historic walls, gates, tombs, temples, palaces, gardens, paintings, and precious artifacts in China
